			"styles": "\n\t/* comment before the direction */\n\tp:dir(/* c1 */ ltr) {\n\t\tcolor: red;\n\t}\n\n\t/* comment after the direction */\n\tp:dir(rtl /* c2 */) {\n\t\tcolor: blue;\n\t}\n\n\t/* comment before the language */\n\tspan:lang(/* c3 */ en) {\n\t\tfont-family: serif;\n\t}\n\n\t/* comment after the language subtag */\n\tspan:lang(en-US /* c4 */) {\n\t\tfont-family: sans-serif;\n\t}\n",
